## Quick Example

```csharp
public record Person
{
    [Required]
    public string Name { get; init; }
    public int Age { get; init; }
}

// Create an editable form
var editor = host.Hub.Edit(new Person());

// Display results
var result = Controls.Markdown("Form created");

// Combine in a vertical stack
var ui = Controls.Stack()
    .WithArea(editor)
    .WithArea(result);
```

Result: A vertical layout containing an auto-generated form for Person and a markdown display below it.
